# VippsTimer

VippsTimer is a Windows overlay timer built for OBS streams with Vipps-style donations.

## Features
- Countdown timer with red background & turquoise text
- OBS chroma key safe (#000001)
- Last 3 payments overlay
- Top 10 donors (daily)
- Admin control panel
- Sound effects by donation amount
- Click-through overlays
- Window position memory

## Requirements (for source)
- Windows 10/11
- Python 3.11+
- OBS Studio

## How to run from source
```bash
py vippstimer.py
